@startuml
!define ICONS /Users/iworldafric/dev/diagrams/plantuml-stdlib/stdlib/tupadr3
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/bolt.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/brain.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/cog.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/check_circle.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/eye.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/sync.puml
!include ICONS/common.puml

skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #922B21
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #E74C3C
skinparam ActivityFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityFontSize 13
skinparam ActivityArrowColor #F1948A
skinparam ActivityArrowFontColor #1C2833
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #7D6608
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #F4D03F
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityStartColor #2ECC71
skinparam ActivityEndColor #E74C3C
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 12
skinparam Padding 8

title Execution Engine — Data Flow

start

:<$cog> **Action Plan Received**
Structured plan from Deliberation Engine:
{ action_type, params, expected_outcome, confidence };

if (confidence > 0.85?) then (yes — high confidence)
  :<$bolt> **System 1 — Fast Path**
  Pattern-match to cached tool call.
  Execute directly via Claude Code hook.
  Latency < 100ms;
elseif (confidence > 0.50?) then (moderate confidence)
  :<$brain> **System 2 — Deliberate**
  Generate step-by-step reasoning chain.
  Call Claude API (Sonnet 4) for execution plan.
  Execute tool calls sequentially;
else (low confidence)
  :<$cog> **System 3 — Tree Search**
  Generate N candidate action sequences.
  Simulate each via State Predictor.
  Select highest expected-value path;
endif

:<$check_circle> **Tool Execution**
Dispatch selected action to Claude Code engine.
Monitor real-time stdout/stderr stream.
Enforce timeout and resource limits;

:<$eye> **Observation**
Capture tool output as new percept.
Compute outcome vs expected_outcome delta.
Update confidence calibration model;

if (outcome delta > threshold?) then (error)
  :<$sync> **Error Recovery**
  Log failure to Episodic Memory.
  Increment error counter for this action class.
  Re-plan with error context added to prompt;
  stop
else (success)
  :<$check_circle> **Result Stored**
  Persist success trace to Episodic Memory.
  Update Procedural Memory if novel technique used.
  Return outcome to Deliberation Engine;
  stop
endif
@enduml
